程投入，「呢個病毒係非常之狡猾，佢不斷咁變化，所以各國政府喺應對時都要不斷總結經驗、不斷完善，將疫情影響減到最低。我可以講，我同我嘅同事都係本住呢種態度嚟到處理今次疫情。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/46L6NMF66RB2JADFPKDUFN6C7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F46L6NMF66RB2JADFPKDUFN6C7A%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=cd9f43c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2F46L6NMF66RB2JADFPKDUFN6C7A%2F&h=09916301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/46L6NMF66RB2JADFPKDUFN6C7A/</a>"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T12:53:24.000Z","msg":"呢個八婆都好狡猾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}